13:06.083 --> 13:07.083
(VACUUMING)

13:11.792 --> 13:13.584
- I knew you'd
- be back, Bertie.

13:13.626 --> 13:15.876
They always come back.

13:15.918 --> 13:17.751
- Usually because of
- an iron-clad pre-nup.

13:19.792 --> 13:21.709
I'm sick of posing!

13:21.751 --> 13:22.793
This is why people

13:22.794 --> 13:23.834
invented cameras!

13:23.876 --> 13:25.000
Patience!

13:25.834 --> 13:27.000
Et voila!

13:28.125 --> 13:29.792
Why am I holding you?

13:29.834 --> 13:31.792
- Because every pirate
- needs a little booty.

13:34.125 --> 13:36.000
I'd rather walk the plank.

13:38.000 --> 13:39.727
- Now, give that to me,
- I'm going to burn it.

13:39.751 --> 13:40.918
Absolutely not!

13:40.959 --> 13:42.792
- This painting will
- not be burned

13:42.834 --> 13:44.143
- Unless your - smoldering gaze
- Sets it afire!

13:44.167 --> 13:45.167
(CHUCKLES)

13:46.083 --> 13:47.626
One, ew!

13:47.667 --> 13:49.250
- Two, give it!
- Ooh! Ooh!

13:49.292 --> 13:50.876
- Give it!
- (CHUCKLING)

13:50.918 --> 13:52.272
Give it!

13:52.273 --> 13:53.626
If you want it,

13:50.918 --> 13:53.626
come and get it!

13:53.667 --> 13:54.834
- (CHORTLES)
- (GRUNTS)

13:54.876 --> 13:56.834
Oh! Oh!

13:56.876 --> 13:58.709
- Oh! Oh! Oh!
- (CHUCKLES)

13:58.751 --> 13:59.897
Oh, these shorts

13:59.898 --> 14:01.042
are so tight!

14:01.083 --> 14:02.083
(SHRIEKS)

14:05.083 --> 14:06.834
(KNOCKING ON DOOR)

14:06.876 --> 14:09.042
Hello? Bertram?

14:09.083 --> 14:10.959
- You just seemed
- a little sad earlier...

14:11.000 --> 14:12.876
(MRS. CHESTERFIELD CHUCKLES)

14:15.167 --> 14:17.125
- I'm so tired.
- (MOCK PANTING)

14:17.167 --> 14:18.292
(LAUGHING)

14:18.334 --> 14:19.543
Give me that!

14:19.544 --> 14:20.751
You drive me crazy!

14:20.792 --> 14:22.959
The feeling is mutual!

14:23.000 --> 14:24.042
(GIGGLING)

14:24.083 --> 14:25.626
Okay. Clearly I misread

14:25.627 --> 14:27.167
those sad vibes.

